summary: Talking seriously, I’m not against the fan theories pertaining the sequel of Breath of the Wild. Theorizing is one of the most...
body:
Talking seriously, I’m not against the fan theories pertaining the sequel of Breath of the Wild. Theorizing is one of the most fun parts of any fandom.

I just think we need to keep things in perspective: Nintendo has revealed very little concrete information about the game and we are basing our theories mostly on speculation and wishful thinking, so it’s likely many fan theories will not come to pass.

Now, by all means, continue with the analysis and the speculation. Just keep in mind that as more information about the game gets released, certain expectations will be dashed, so don’t get too sad or angered if your favorite theory doesn’t come to pass.
